details.place_name: Publix Super Market at Arboretum Park
details.description: Save on your favorite products and enjoy award-winning service at Publix Super Market at Arboretum Park. Shop our wide selection of high-quality meats, local produce, sustainably sourced seafood, and more. Try our signature items such as our Deli subs and Bakery cakes. Looking for something special? Our friendly associates are happy to help. Visit our Charlotte, NC store and see why shopping here is a pleasure.

reviews_data.review_text: New Publix! Great service as always

Everyone working at the deli moves at a glacier pace, placed an order for a sub pick up for my lunch break and wasted over 15 minutes just standing waiting for them to be done. While workers just argued over who had to do what, extremely unprofessional to watch.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Juan, can you please reach out to our Customer Care line at 1-800-242-1227, or private message us on Facebook here: http://spr.ly/6268AWhnC, we will be happy to help get this concern addressed with the Store Manager.

reviews_data.review_text: they are nice people working and clean

I shopped here for the first time tonight, and overall - it is okay. The store is very clean and the employees were helpful, although it feels a bit smaller than the one in Matthews. The biggest concern I have is for people who plan to shop at night here - I was a bit shocked that the parking deck was so dimly lit, especially since it is a brand new store. Hopefully this will be addressed soon, as it could be a major safety concern.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi David, can you please reach out to our Customer Care line at 1-800-242-1227, or private message us on Facebook here: http://spr.ly/6264AW7Q4, we will be happy to help get this concern addressed with the Store Manager.

reviews_data.review_text: Always South Charlotte has a new Publix. Literally there is another Publix on Carmel Commons. This one is across the street from Walmart will have to use a crosswalk every time. Every week good deals friendly staff members. Saw some people help out from other stores. I will come here whenever I'm in the area! Only thing I didn't like is that the parking deck was at the upper level and the store is on the lower level no elevators just stairs.

Beautiful store! Well organized and well laid out, with plenty of parking. The associates are very friendly, in particular Doug went above and beyond in helping me find what I needed for my dinner recipe. Highly recommend this store and will be coming back!
Brand New Publix Will Be Opening On A Opening Date Is: Saturday September 20, 2025!!!
